  "name": "Pact of the Tome",
  "ownership": {
    "default": 0
  },
  "type": "feat",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your patron gives you a grimoire called a Book of Shadows. When you gain this feature, choose three at-wills from any class's power list (the three needn't be from the same list). While the book is on your person, you can cast those at-wills at will. They don't count against your number of at-wills known. If they don't appear on the warlock power list, they are nonetheless warlock powers for you.</p><p>If you lose your Book of Shadows, you can perform a 1-hour ceremony to receive a replacement from your patron. This ceremony can be performed during a short or long rest, and it destroys the previous book. The book turns to ash when you die.</p>",
